1
B. The resolution to reduce the special levy, as provided for
1
2
in subsection A of this section, shall include the following
2
3
information:
3
4
1. The current and proposed millage rate;
4
5
2. Findings that the proposed millage rate provides sufficient
5
6
funding for the library;
6
7
3. A determination that the reduction is in the best interests
7
8
of the taxpayers in the county; and
8
9
4. The effective tax year of the levy reduction.
9
10
SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
